

======= SQL Functions ===========

DUAL table  <- its a Virtual table, generally used to compelete select query, its optional.

1.  NOW()  function

----------------------------------------
mysql> select NOW();
+---------------------+
| NOW()               |
+---------------------+
| 2024-11-18 14:31:32 |
+---------------------+
1 row in set (0.01 sec)


  
mysql> select NOW() from DUAL;
+---------------------+
| NOW()               |
+---------------------+
| 2024-11-18 14:31:58 |
+---------------------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)

---------------------------------------------
mysql> select 2*2;
+-----+
| 2*2 |
+-----+
|   4 |
+-----+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> select 2*2 from Dual;
+-----+
| 2*2 |
+-----+
|   4 |
+-----+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)
